<br>
I must admit though.. exp in these planes are killer. Almost got a full level there in a charm group last nite. If you have never done it before, get 2 enchanters, 2 druids, a cleric and a bard. with 4 pets we where mowing mobs down in seconds for 1% exp each kill. Not to mention it was fun in an insane kinda way.<br>
